Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.42,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.42,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:12.76,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:12.76,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.23,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.23,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.47,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.47,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:01:01.81,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:01:01.81,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:11.28,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:11.28,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:39.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll be commuting here for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:44.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I'll be working with the\Ncompany I just quit from so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First order of business for the future:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Projects begin with networking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And networking begins with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yamada! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please contact me when you decide on a design!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:08.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving already? Why don't you stick around a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a teaching assistant for a lecture at noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:18.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, wait a—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rika-san? Where's Rika-san? Where's Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, not today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.05,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\c&H37419C&\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\fs72\an4\bord1\shad0\3c&H332A32&\pos(524,19)}Disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:32.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was thinking of having lunch with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:32.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs36\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H208ED7&\pos(424,379)}"Eeek! You're twisting me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I did invite her along...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.60,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\bord1.5\fscy90\be1\fs18\c&H9D86E5&\3c&HDFE7E5&\pos(604,94)}The Last Business Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs36\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&)\c&H3AA8E8&}"Please come again."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see that dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how should I explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The dog... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:42.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nomiya-san, about Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set aside that issue for later. Why\Ndon't we talk about the job first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why was Yamada here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to start carrying potteries in our stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we've decided to ask her to come by once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:13.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some rule that says that we need to put\Neverything about Yamada-san through you first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in love shouldn't worry so much\Nabout the woman he turned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:23.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san, what do you think of Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"She's cute..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a puppy or a kitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or like a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh... like a girl, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you just slightly interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.79,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\3c&H425E75&\bord0.01\be1\fs26\fscy50\c&H4A617B&\pos(270,78)}H\Ne\Nl\Np
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.50,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.29,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it, Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say, Mayama, do I really look all that evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:02.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I see you as the type who's just interested in Yamada\Nto take her, have your way with her, and toss her aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch. You're still bitter that I took her out to eat soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to take her so abruptly to Nagano of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I kind of wanted to go somewhere far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With a sleeping girl in your passenger seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And not to take her somewhere where you could be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:19.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never felt that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what if Yamada had answered "udon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've headed to Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.50,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\fsp-1\b0\bord2\3c&HE7F0F7&\pos(165,43)\c&H514F4F&}Shikoku
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.50,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\fsp-1\b0\bord2\3c&HE7F0F7&\c&H514F4F&\pos(689,347)}Haneda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, when you say udon, you gotta go to Takamatsu in Shikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, that's precisely why I can't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:48.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, that image is burned into my mind as if in slow motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy with work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I finally understand the carelessness that I sense in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:05.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason I'm attracted to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, the reason why I'm afraid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:16.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd act a little more seriously, I wouldn't\Nhave to be acting like such an idiot, Nomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The time that had stopped began to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It never even slowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:13.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Time was streaming down, just like a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:20.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole year, while I had been simply standing still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The rice cooked itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the rice is really cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want dinner? Or a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want me—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:47.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, here's some of those\Nsweet n' sour meatballs that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bon appétit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:56.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This table setting really feels like it's from the Showa period...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, where did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was so excited that we could eat dinner together again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:04.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I bought the whole set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}entire {\i0}set?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:08.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:13.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you came to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That you came to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:27.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru told me that you were saying, "You idiot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:31.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That you were screaming, "What the hell are you thinking?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me, "To think you actually have friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:43.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking this whole time that something within\Nme would come to an end once you returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:50.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was scared, that I didn't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:57.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, God, why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd be happy to be able to eat dinner with him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is! The resupply troop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Morita-san all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:32.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the annual flower-watching recital\Nwould be canceled on its ninth performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a heartbreaking accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:40.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to appear magnificently from\Nthe air, he even rented a crane...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:46.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that the bungee rope was just a little too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I've heard, he was slammed\Ninto the ground seven or eight times...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That many times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:56.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this melody?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:15.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zu-zundo, zundoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:18.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zu-zundo, zundoko, zundoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't given up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone's being touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the accident was choreographed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. His arm was bent the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Rika-san? Where's Rika-san? Where's Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:35.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs33\fsp6\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H3294D1&\pos(668,78)}"The cherry blossoms\Nare pretty, aren't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, geez... drunk already, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:40.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:40.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san won't be coming. She doesn't like things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's a flower-watching and you're hogging her to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ever hog her to myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:49.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you want to! You want to hog her all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... think I'll go home soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:54.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:56.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:58.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:03.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama! Yamada-san is trying to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, she's half-bawling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamada, don't go home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with everyone once this is over, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll go back to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:31.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then why don't you just go back already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ow, ow, h-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My car's gonna get towed, so I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just throw the others into a taxi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting along as usual, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're not getting along!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, this girl's drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "this girl"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:55.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I drive you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want to go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:05.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:23.41,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}boku no jounetsu wa imaya
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:23.41,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}My passion has now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:36.22,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}nagashita hazu no namida yori tsumetakunatte shimatta
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:36.22,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Grown colder than the tears that I was supposed to have shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:38.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada... Nomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:45.52,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}donna hito yori mo umaku
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:45.52,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}I've become able to fake myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:49.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama always loses sight of me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:58.49,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}jibun no koto o itsuwareru chikara wo motte shimatta
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:58.49,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really easily like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:55.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll probably keep doing it... forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:04.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it irritates me to be used for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:12.09,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}daiji na kotoba o nando mo iouto shite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:12.09,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I tried to say those important words many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Nomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:16.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that Mayama would come chasing\Nafter you, if you did something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:20.31,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}suikomu iki wa mune no tochuu de tsukaeta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:20.31,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But the air that I breathe in gets stuck in the middle of my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I'll go home, after all—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me to take you somewhere, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:30.57,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}donna kotoba de kimi ni tsutaereba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:30.57,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}What words should I use to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please relax your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:33.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll accompany you... wherever you'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:35.40,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}hakidasu koe wa itsumo tochuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:35.40,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}The voice that spills out always, in the middle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go to Nagano again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nomiya-san, I need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:59.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your game of tag over now, since\NMayama didn't chase after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A game of tag? It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about Rika-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:14.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just waiting for them to fall apart, while\Nyou complain and sulk, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you, Nomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:19.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you used me to attract Mayama's attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure being selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:30.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer will you keep testing Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do understand your position...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An unrequited love that's emerged is unproductive, but simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:39.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your infatuation makes him feel guilty, so he's nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And nothing worse could possibly happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor will you be hurt anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:01.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently driving and cannot answer your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:04.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's put his phone on drive mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yamada, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her running away earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:11.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been kidnapped, by this scary person from my old job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not injured, are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Actually, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:30.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to karaoke next. Do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:34.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you still haven't sung enough, Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I'll leave Yamada to you guys then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the deal is, but don't go telling everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. It might trouble Yamada later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you're way too overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yamada-san? And Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs33\fsp6\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(144,52)\c&H018FE5&}"I'm sleepy."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the two of them ran off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they went to Sendai this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he'll be bringing back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a guy is Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:41.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see... he's good at his job, refreshing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Handsome, popular with girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, he's a nice guy then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so unhappy with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He also never lets us on to what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:01.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he operates on something other than his real desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you two are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I mean, isn't he supposed to be handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:14.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you two are the same type, but you're\Nat different stages of development.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda like how a suit is a suit, even if one's a\Nluxury brand and the other's 500 yen a pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:25.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... aren't you guys getting carried away with the\Nexample and forgetting to consider my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:28.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, your names are the same, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi and Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fscy87\bord3\fnTimes New Roman\3c&HE6FFFF&\c&H102E2C&\shad0\pos(242,33)}Craftsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fscy87\bord3\fnTimes New Roman\3c&HE6FFFF&\c&H102E2C&\shad0\pos(613,33)}Master
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs46\c&H091C1B&\bord0.1\be1\shad3\pos(325,41)\4a&H64&\4c&H1C4D4C&}Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.47,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs46\bord0.1\be1\shad3\pos(325,41)\4a&H64&\c&HFBFFFE&\3c&HEBEBEB&\4c&H943E35&}Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs46\c&H091C1B&\bord0.1\be1\shad3\pos(325,41)\4a&H64&\4c&H1C4D4C&}Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:30.43,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs46\c&H091C1B&\bord0.1\be1\shad3\4a&H64&\4c&H1C4D4C&\pos(542,41)}Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.18,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs46\bord0.1\be1\shad3\pos(542,41)\4a&H64&\c&HFBFFFE&\3c&HEBEBEB&\4c&H943E35&}Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs46\c&H091C1B&\bord0.1\be1\shad3\4a&H64&\4c&H1C4D4C&\pos(542,41)}Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Takumi" spelled as "master" and "Takumi"\Nspelled as "craftsmanship"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge difference in character!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad for Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was born pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:49.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's had multiple defensive barriers\Nput up by her numerous knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ayu is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:51.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're not getting a single step closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:54.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And while no one can step in, she's been isolated in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}La-la-la-la-la, I want to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:01.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mayama, could it be that you don't like Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be frank, he's hard to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two really are alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya was calling you an irritating brat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:16.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know of his true intentions, but he\Nmight not be as evil as you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:21.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if that's not the case, then you'd be considered evil, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are alike, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:27.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ayu... all because you fell in love with a man like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:35.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, after 11 we only offer takeouts. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:39.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, one of every cake to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And two tall cappucinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:51.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go move the car really quick, so can you pay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little windy, but let's eat outside\Nwhere we can see the ferris wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bench and a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised that the floor became cushiony all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a different building starting from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:41.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The interior of this building was the\Nfirst big work I did at my old job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:47.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The design itself was by a designer out in California,\Nso I only worked on the construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there wasn't much time between the completion\Nof the building itself and the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up sleeping in a sleeping bag\Non the floor for the last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would fall asleep around dawn, looking out at that ferris wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes come here by myself to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It clears my mind when I stare at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously wished...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:24.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That the world would disappear before we got off the ferris wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it about Mayama that you like, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:52.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If my love for him is genuine, I should\Nbe able to wish for his happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I... just like you said in the car earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had honestly... been hoping they'd fall apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:07.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole time... this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:11.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:37.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:50.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I sure saw some amazing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Various things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even called home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Nomiya-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat breakfast first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:10.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And since we came all the way out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride that thing.
